<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快醒醒！求你了！ 听到的话请说句话！”孩子们一遍又一遍地说着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“用牛奶弄湿他的耳朵。”鲍比建议说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人晕倒时，用香水这么做有用，我觉得牛奶应该也可以。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，他们用牛奶弄湿了男孩儿的耳朵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>隧道里很黑。彼得的蜡烛已经很短了，光也很弱了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“求求你睁开眼睛吧！”菲利斯说，“我觉得他已经死了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他没死！”鲍比坚持说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得摇了摇男孩儿的胳膊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>慢慢地，男孩儿睁开眼睛，轻轻地呼出一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，他没死！”菲利斯喊，“我就知道他没死！”她哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别哭了，我没事。”男孩儿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“菲利斯，安静点儿。”彼得说，“喝点儿这个。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是什么？”男孩儿问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是牛奶。”彼得说，“别担心。我们会帮你的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是男孩儿喝了点儿牛奶。孩子们安静地看着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他喝完牛奶就没事了。”彼得小声对姐妹们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105278</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我好多了。”男孩儿说。他想动，但是发出了一声呻吟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我……我觉得我的腿断了。”他慢慢地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你摔倒了吗？”菲利斯问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我被一根电线绊倒了。”男孩儿解释说，“我站不起来，所以坐下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是真的很疼。你们是怎么过来的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们看到你们一起跑进了隧道。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们也看到大家跑出了隧道——除了你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以我们过来救你。”彼得自豪地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153011</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157078</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们真的很勇敢！”男孩儿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157078</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这没什么。”彼得说，“我们扶着你的话，你能走吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164147</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以试试。”男孩儿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他试了一下，但他只能一只脚站着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我得坐下来。太疼了。”他坐下不久就睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们互相看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们去找人。”鲍比说，“我留下。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得看上去很担心。“还是我留下，你和菲利斯去吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，你和菲利斯去。”鲍比说，“把你的刀给我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205146</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在他醒来之前，我要把他的靴子割开。你们快去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205146</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比看着他们离开，然后把短短的蜡烛放在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在的你，不是傻丫头 ！”她自言自语地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果有人叫鲍比“傻丫头”，她总是非常生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但她生自己的气时，也会这样叫自己。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拔出小刀，割开男孩儿的靴子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比想脱下他的袜子，但是他的腿太肿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>隧道里好像更黑了。一切看上去都很不真实。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“傻丫头。”鲍比又说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看着男孩儿的腿。“应该在下面垫一个软的东西。”她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想起了自己的衬裙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她小心地把衬裙脱下来，垫在男孩儿的腿下面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268145</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来就只能等了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>